*% ========== General Information ==========

*FileSystem: True
*DefaultResolution: 1200dpi
*Throughput: "80"
*LanguageLevel: "3"
*TTRasterizer: Type42
*ColorDevice: True
*DefaultColorSpace: CMYK
*Reset: "
   count 0 eq
   { false } { true exch startjob } ifelse
   not { (WARNING: Cannot reset printer.) =
            (Missing or invalid password.) =
            (Please contact the author of this software.) = flush quit
          } if
   systemdict /quit get exec
   (WARNING: Printer Reset Failed.) = flush
"
*End
*ExitServer: "
   count 0 eq
   { false } { true exch startjob } ifelse
   not { (WARNING: Cannot modify initial VM.) =
            (Missing or invalid password.) =
            (Please contact the author of this software.) = flush quit
          } if
"
*End
*Password: "0"
*FreeVM: "16632226"
*PrintPSErrors: True
*AccurateScreensSupport: True
*ContoneOnly: True
*FCacheSize None: 524288
*RequiresPageRegion All: True
*LandscapeOrientation: Plus90




*% ========== Mixed Media ==========

*% ****** Enable MM1.2 & MM1.3
*% ****** Enable MM1.3
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFMixedMedia:string]
*%EFIKeyAttribute [EFMixedMedia][version:13]
*%EFIValue [EFMixedMedia:CWS]
*%EFIValue [EFMixedMedia:driver]
*% ***** Enable MM1.2
*% *****
*% ***** Enable chapters
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFEnableChapter:string]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableChapter:CWS]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableChapter:driver]
*% ***** Enable Subset finishing
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFEnableSubsetFinishing:string]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableSubsetFinishing:CWS]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableSubsetFinishing:driver]
*% ***** Enable Mixed Media Insertions
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFEnableMixedMediaInsertion:string]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableMixedMediaInsertion:CWS]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableMixedMediaInsertion:driver]
*% ***** Enable Constraint Enforcement
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFMixedMediaEnforceConstraints:string]
*%EFIValue [EFMixedMediaEnforceConstraints:CWS]
*%EFIValue [EFMixedMediaEnforceConstraints:driver]
*% ***** Enable Cover Page
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFEnableMixedMediaCoverPages:string]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableMixedMediaCoverPages:CWS]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableMixedMediaCoverPages:driver]
*% ***** Enable Tab Handling
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFEnableMixedMediaTabs:string]
*%EFIValue [EFEnableMixedMediaTabs:CWS]




*% ========== Paper Catalog ==========

*% ***** Enable Paper Catalog 3.5
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFPaperCatalog:string]
*%EFIKeyAttribute [EFPaperCatalog][version:35]
*%EFIValue [EFPaperCatalog:CWS]
*%EFIValue [EFPaperCatalog:driver]
*%EFILocal [EFPaperCatalog:Paper Catalog]
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFPCName:string]
*%EFIEScope [column|joblog|Rerip]
*%EFIKeyAttribute [EFPCName][polymorphic:yes]
*%EFILocal [EFPCName:Paper Catalog Name]
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFPCMGID:string]
*%EFIEScope [Rerip]
*%EFIKeyAttribute [EFPCMGID][polymorphic:yes]
*%EFILocal [EFPCMGID:Paper Catalog Group ID]
*%EFIKey [ : ][EFPCMID:string]
*%EFIEScope [Rerip]
*%EFIKeyAttribute [EFPCMID][polymorphic:yes]
*%EFILocal [EFPCMID:Paper Catalog ID]




*% ========== UI Menus ==========

*%EFIFlags *EFIPrintTime APPE|Column|Command|Impose
*%EFIGroup *EFIPrintTime FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *EFIPrintTime/Schedule printing:31:UTF8

*%EFIFlags *EFUserAuthName APPE|Impose
*%EFIGroup *EFUserAuthName FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *EFUserAuthName/User name:64:UTF8
*%EFUserAuthName: " /XJXsetUserName where { pop (<*EFUserAuthName>) XJXsetUserName} if "

*%EFIFlags *EFUserAuthPwd APPE|Impose
*%EFIGroup *EFUserAuthPwd FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *EFUserAuthPwd/Password:64:Encrypt|Password|UTF8
*%EFUserAuthPwd: " /XJXsetAccessCode where { pop (<*EFUserAuthPwd>) XJXsetAccessCode} if "

*%EFIFlags *Notes1 APPE|Column|Command|Impose|SummaryPane
*%EFIGroup *Notes1 FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *Notes1/Notes 1:31:PopupJN|UTF8
*%Notes1: "%%EFICustom1: <*Notes1> "

*%EFIFlags *Notes2 APPE|Column|Command|Impose|SummaryPane
*%EFIGroup *Notes2 FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *Notes2/Notes 2:31:PopupJN|UTF8
*%Notes2: "%%EFICustom2: <*Notes2> "

*%EFIFlags *Instruct APPE|Column|Command|Impose|SummaryPane
*%EFIGroup *Instruct FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *Instruct/Instructions:127:UTF8
*%Instruct: "%%EFICustom3: <*Instruct> "

*%EFIFlags *Resume APPE|Impose
*%EFIGroup *Resume FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *Resume/Secure print:31:LCD|NoComma|Password|Resume|UTF8
*%Resume: "%%PersPassword: <*Resume> "

*%EFIFlags *EFPersUserID APPE|Column|Command|Impose|Joblog
*%EFIGroup *EFPersUserID FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *EFPersUserID/Account name:8:Alpha|Numeric|PopupJN|UTF8
*%EFPersUserID: " /XJXsetUserID where { pop (<*EFPersUserID>) XJXsetUserID} if "

*%EFIFlags *EFPersUserPWD APPE|Command|Impose|Joblog
*%EFIGroup *EFPersUserPWD FPJobInfo/Job Info
*%EFIJobNote *EFPersUserPWD/Account password:8:Alpha|Numeric|Password|PopupJN|UTF8
*%EFPersUserPWD: " /XJXsetUserPWD where { pop (<*EFPersUserPWD>) XJXsetUserPWD} if "

*%EFIFlags *EFRaster APPE|Column|Impose
*%EFIGroup *EFRaster FPJobInfo/Job Info
*OpenUI *EFRaster/Print queue action:PickOne
*OrderDependency: 65.0 AnySetup *EFRaster
*DefaultEFRaster: False
*EFRaster False/Print: " userdict /XJXsetraster known { 0 XJXsetraster } if "
*EFRaster True/Print and hold: " userdict /XJXsetraster known { 1 XJXsetraster } if "
*EFRaster RipNHold/Process and hold: " userdict /XJXsetraster known { 2 XJXsetraster } if "
*EFRaster Hold/Hold: " userdict /XJXsetraster known { 4 XJXsetraster } if "
*EFRaster PrintNDelete/Print and delete: " userdict /XJXsetraster known { 3 XJXsetraster } if "
*CloseUI: *EFRaster

*%EFIFlags *EFControlBar APPE|Command|DevDict|Dynamic|EFGAEmbeddedFeatureOpt_ColorRight|Impose|Rerip
*%EFIGroup *EFControlBar FPJobInfo/Job Info
*OpenUI *EFControlBar/Control Bar:PickOne
*OrderDependency: 58.4 AnySetup *EFControlBar
*DefaultEFControlBar: False
*EFControlBar False/Off: " userdict /XJXsetControlBar known { (False) XJXsetControlBar } if "
*EFControlBar Default/Fiery: " userdict /XJXsetControlBar known { (Fiery) XJXsetControlBar } if "
*CloseUI: *EFControlBar

*%EFIFlags *EFPostFlight APPE|Command|EFGAEmbeddedFeatureOpt_ColorRight|Impose|Rerip
*%EFIGroup *EFPostFlight FPJobInfo/Job Info
*OpenUI *EFPostFlight/Postflight:PickOne
*OrderDependency: 62.0 AnySetup *EFPostFlight
*DefaultEFPostFlight: False
*EFPostFlight False/Off: " /XJXSetPostFlight where { pop 0 XJXSetPostFlight } if "
*EFPostFlight ReportConcise/Concise report: " /XJXSetPostFlight where { pop 9 XJXSetPostFlight } if "
*EFPostFlight TestPage/Test page: " /XJXSetPostFlight where { pop 5 XJXSetPostFlight } if "
*EFPostFlight ColorCodedJob/Color-coded pages: " /XJXSetPostFlight where { pop 3 XJXSetPostFlight } if "
*EFPostFlight All/All components: " /XJXSetPostFlight where { pop 31 XJXSetPostFlight } if "
*CloseUI: *EFPostFlight

*%EFIFlags *EFDisplayJobTracking Impose|SummaryPane
*%EFIGroup *EFDisplayJobTracking FPJobInfo/Job Info
*OpenUI *EFDisplayJobTracking/Enable job tracking:Boolean
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *EFDisplayJobTracking
*DefaultEFDisplayJobTracking: False
*EFDisplayJobTracking False/Off: " userdict /EFI_Props known { << /EFI_PgTkt [ (EFDisplayJobTracking) (False) ] >> EFI_Props } if "
*End
*EFDisplayJobTracking True/On: " userdict /EFI_Props known { << /EFI_PgTkt [ (EFDisplayJobTracking) (True) ] >> EFI_Props } if "
*End
*CloseUI: *EFDisplayJobTracking

*%EFIFlags *EFAccountSetting Impose
