*OpenUI *EFAccountSetting/AccountSettings:PickOne
*OrderDependency: 50.0 AnySetup *EFAccountSetting
*DefaultEFAccountSetting: AlwaysEnter
*EFAccountSetting AlwaysEnter/Allow entry of account information: " userdict /EFI_Props known { << /EFI_PgTkt [ (EFAccountSetting) (AlwaysEnter) ] >> EFI_Props } if "
*EFAccountSetting AlwaysUseLast/Use last entered account information: " userdict /EFI_Props known { << /EFI_PgTkt [ (EFAccountSetting) (AlwaysUseLast) ] >> EFI_Props } if "
*CloseUI: *EFAccountSetting

*%EFIFlags *EFAccountShowLast Impose
