*%EFIFlags *EFResolution APPE|Command|DevDict|Dynamic|Impose|Rerip|Setup|SummaryPane
*%EFIGroup *EFResolution FPImage/Image
*OpenUI *EFResolution/Resolution:PickOne
*OrderDependency: 12.0 AnySetup *EFResolution
*DefaultEFResolution: 1200x1200dpi
*EFResolution 1200x1200dpi/1200 dpi: " /XJXsetresolution where { pop ([1200 1200]) XJXsetresolution } if "
*EFResolution 600x600dpi/600 dpi: " /XJXsetresolution where { pop ([600 600]) XJXsetresolution } if "
*?EFResolution: "
save
    initgraphics
    0 0 moveto currentpoint matrix defaultmatrix transform
  0 72 lineto currentpoint matrix defaultmatrix transform
  3 -1 roll sub dup mul
  3 1 roll exch sub dup mul
  add sqrt round cvi
  10 string cvs print (dpi) = flush
restore "
*End
*CloseUI: *EFResolution

